lockquote><br />\n<br />\n無689就有uber喇，on9仔"},{"pid":"6f9b603469eb39032b08d5a8e67f4f6f275292fe","tid":105081,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一向唔睇好，得啖笑，幾時到香港。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無689就有uber喇，on9仔</blockquote><br />\n香港跟大陸行<br />\n滴滴收購完uber, 已經算係拿法化"},{"pid":"99fb52b0227da8e825c37afa5b3327eb069725f4","tid":105081,"uid":32252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"去四日台北 除咗一啲好近既地方搭捷運 其他都係uber出入 真係好平 平過搭的士好多 真係好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b95e75f751fdc2eedf4fa7df3aba16a10a058ca","tid":105081,"uid":79016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:33:15.000Z","msg":"一日有的士狗 都繼續搭uber"},{"pid":"c15b860828004ece65560306f67efbfe8a515b2a","tid":105081,"uid":32252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:02:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一日有的士狗 都繼續搭uber</blockquote><br />\n台灣uber司機話都係政府同的士聯手 搞到無得做"},{"pid":"e8ae818d29a8d31e2a74b81dce73cdb394ea6c0c","tid":105081,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一日有的士狗 都繼續搭uber</blockquote><br />\n台灣uber司機話都係政府同的士聯手 搞到無得做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講到尾係咩人去做的士佬<br />\n<br />\n你睇日本，乜都唔駛做就已經搞掂你<br />\n<br />\n但你香港嘅的士司機有日本運將嘅quality 咩"},{"pid":"d9752dd15e6247f35bbe0667b18f9cea01194657","tid":105081,"uid":22402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:39:45.000Z","msg":"香港Uber有個敗點係小車<br />\n經常要等10分鐘兼有加乘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要等既話我寧願坐的士算"},{"pid":"58dcd6765d0216765d68a9246f4d7812532a7a7e","tid":105081,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T19:36:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一日有的士狗 都繼續搭uber</blockquote><br />\n台灣uber司機話都係政府同的士聯手 搞到無得做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講到尾係咩人去做的士佬<br />\n<br />\n你睇日本，乜都唔駛做就已經搞掂你<br />\n<br />\n但你香港嘅的士司機有日本運將嘅quality 咩</blockquote><br />\n唔好話日本，台灣好多司機都好nice, 又教你點去玩，又唔會呃遊客，可能都有害群之馬，但一定比香港少"},{"pid":"86e736308d86704ced2c3590c0683757e0211b7f","tid":105081,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T23:35:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港Uber有個敗點係小車<br />\n經常要等10分鐘兼有加乘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要等既話我寧願坐的士算</blockquote><br />\n仲有gogo van<br />\n平d同bb車唔洗收"},{"pid":"b045bd747a2072bcf8bea0f9e524eed19d2f5db5","tid":105081,"uid":72,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:22:39.000Z","msg":"台灣搭uber真係好方便又平，我識個台灣朋友佢做司機，高峰期可以每個月賺5皮台幣"},{"pid":"b3e5308835c252bfe9ea948a475ef7862b573a18","tid":105081,"uid":17443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣搭uber真係好方便又平，我識個台灣朋友佢做司機，高峰期可以每個月賺5皮台幣</blockquote><br />\n香港高峰期每月都賺5皮港幣"},{"pid":"9fef39961a3194b9f9f46259ec96112511f0e9dd","tid":105081,"uid":74192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"上兩個月去台中日日坐uber<br />\n又平又多車，司機又nice<br />\n聽到我香港黎仲同我講太陽花成功過佔中"},{"pid":"a0cf6e960627a0fe58199b0d29ff9040412aa22f","tid":105081,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:24:39.000Z","msg":"民進黨靠的士司機起家, 太運花學運都係靠的士司機通風報信<br />\n而加民進黨執政要造低 Uber, 係好正常既事<br />\n<br />\n台灣既官商鄉黑遠比我地想像中嚴重, 覺得香港污煙瘴氣而移民台灣既香港人, <br />\n我只可以講佢地係戇鳩."},{"pid":"b0c3b76be34934ff1971a9672da4cb1ce7e869c1","tid":105081,"uid":32252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:41:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>民進黨靠的士司機起家, 太運花學運都係靠的士司機通風報信<br />\n而加民進黨執政要造低 Uber, 係好正常既事<br />\n<br />\n台灣既官商鄉黑遠比我地想像中嚴重, 覺得香港污煙瘴氣而移民台灣既香港人, <br />\n我只可以講佢地係戇鳩.</blockquote><br />\nAgger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}